1:Description
Objective: Set up the email trigger for the last milestone completion so that users who earn $160 receive an email with a $100 discount code.
Acceptance criteria:
 >An email is successfully sent to the user upon reaching the last milestone ($160)
 >The email contains the $100 discount code
 >The discount code is delivered to the correct user email address

2:Objective: Set up the email trigger for the first milestone completion so that users who earn $15 receive a surprise gift email with a $5 discount code.

Acceptance criteria:
>An email is successfully sent to the user upon reaching the first milestone ($15)
>The email contains the $5 discount code
>The discount code is delivered to the correct user email address

3:Objective: Set up the email trigger for the completion of a game step so that users are notified each time they complete a step towards earning their reward.

Acceptance criteria:
>An email is successfully sent to the user upon completing a game step
>The email contains the correct content and is delivered to the user's email address

4:Objective: Set up the Discount Code Generation API so that discount codes can be automatically generated and sent to users when they reach a milestone.

Acceptance criteria:
>A $5 discount code is successfully generated when a user reaches the first milestone ($15)
>A $100 discount code is successfully generated when a user reaches the last milestone ($160)
>Generated discount codes are valid and can be applied on the Goli store